## CORE COMPONENTS & RESPONSIBILITIES

### CLI Layer (`indexed/src/indexed/`)

**Responsibility:** User interface, command parsing, output formatting, user interactions.

#### Components

| Component | Purpose |
|-----------|---------|
| `app.py` | Main Typer application, global flags, logging initialization |
| `knowledge/commands/` | Index operations: create, search, inspect, update, remove |
| `config/cli.py` | Configuration management: get, set, validate, delete |
| `mcp/server.py` | FastMCP server implementation for AI agent integration |
| `utils/` | Rich UI components, progress bars, theming, logging |

#### Responsibilities

- Parse user commands and options
- Initialize logging and configuration
- Format and display results (plain text, JSON, tables)
- Handle storage mode resolution (global vs. local)
- Provide Rich UI with progress indicators and error feedback
- Support both verbose and quiet modes

### Service Layer (`packages/indexed-core/src/core/v1/`)

**Responsibility:** Business logic, orchestration, high-level operations.

#### Components

| Component | Type | Purpose |
|-----------|------|---------|
| `collection_service` | Functions | Stateless operations: create(), update(), clear() |
| `SearchService` | Class | Semantic search with cached searcher instances |
| `InspectService` | Class | Collection metadata and status inspection |
| `Index` | Facade | High-level API for library users |

#### Responsibilities

- Orchestrate collection creation with config validation
- Manage searcher caching to avoid redundant index loading
- Provide collection status and metadata inspection
- Support both single and multi-collection search
- Implement validation and error handling
- Enable library usage via Index facade

### Engine Layer (`packages/indexed-core/src/core/v1/engine/`)

**Responsibility:** Core indexing, search algorithms, persistence.

#### Components

| Component | Purpose |
|-----------|---------|
| `DocumentCollectionCreator` | Orchestrate indexing pipeline |
| `DocumentCollectionSearcher` | Handle search operations with cached indexes |
| `FaissIndexer` | Vector storage and similarity search |
| `SentenceEmbedder` | Text embedding with sentence-transformers |
| `DiskPersister` | Save collections to disk |

#### Responsibilities

- Read documents from sources (via Connectors)
- Convert raw documents to searchable chunks
- Generate vector embeddings for texts
- Create and manage FAISS indexes
- Persist collections and metadata to disk
- Perform similarity search on indexed collections

### Infrastructure

| Component | Package | Responsibility |
|-----------|---------|-----------------|
| `ConfigService` | indexed-config | TOML config loading, validation, merging |
| `Connectors` | indexed-connectors | Document reading from Jira, Confluence, files |
| `FAISS Indexes` | indexed-core | Vector storage and similarity search |
| `Disk Storage` | indexed-core | Collection directory structure and files |

